research_municipality_step.notes: The elected officials for Lone Star City, TX, were identified using information from the Texas Municipal League City Officials Directory, the Texas State Directory Online, and the official results of the May 4, 2024 election. Brianna McClain is consistently listed as Mayor. Dawn Fergurson Allender is listed as Mayor Pro Tem and was elected as an Alderman in the May 2024 election. Jerri Chism and Tony Johnson were also elected as Aldermen in the May 2024 election. Both Mayor and Alderman positions have two-year terms, making the May 2024 election results current for the Alderman roles.
